tc.compiler.tree.visit

Class Encode

  • java.lang.Object
    • tc.compiler.tree.visit.TreeVisitorBase<java.lang.String>
      • tc.compiler.tree.visit.Encode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeVisitor<java.lang.String>

    public final class Encode
extends TreeVisitorBase<java.lang.String>
    Does a traversal of the AST to generate LLVM code to execute the program represented by the AST.

    Uses a String for the type parameter, which usually will be the name of the temporary variable that will contain (at runtime) the result of executing the code for a subtree.
